query:
INSERT INTO question (
                    id,
                    prompt,
                    response_char_limit,
                    response_placeholder_text,
                    allow_anonymous_responses,
                    embed_id
                ) VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4,
                    $5,
                    $6
                ) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                    prompt = $2,
                    response_char_limit = $3,
                    response_placeholder_text = $4,
                    allow_anonymous_responses = $5,
                    embed_id = $6
                RETURNING *
